WEBVTT

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:32.000
"Oh yeah, my wife, Toby."

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:36.656
They had graduated
together from Juilliard,

00:06:36.680 --> 00:06:40.216
and she had given up her job
as a concert violinist

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:41.616
to be his coach,

00:06:41.640 --> 00:06:43.096
sitting in the audience,

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:45.496
observing him and giving him feedback.

00:06:45.520 --> 00:06:48.416
"Itzhak, in that middle section,

00:06:48.440 --> 00:06:50.600
you know you sounded
a little bit mechanical.

00:06:51.080 --> 00:06:53.020
What can you differently next time?"

00:06:54.240 --> 00:06:57.400
It was crucial to everything
he became, he said.

00:06:58.840 --> 00:07:03.080
Turns out there are numerous problems
in making it on your own.